<h1>Van &#38; LGV accident repairs, North West and Wirral</h1>

<p>Our workshop in the Wirral caters for the lighter side of commercial vehicles, from car-derived vans up to large vans with long wheel-bases and high roofs. We repair minor dents and scrapes, carry out refurbishments, and heavy smash repairs.</p>
</div>

<div>
<h2>Replacement vehicles</h2>

<p>If you&#8217;re self-employed with only one vehicle and in the North West and Wirral, we understand its importance to your business. We will help with your accident claim and repair your vehicle quickly, sourcing a replacement if needed. For larger fleets, we handle all accident management needs nationwide.</p>
</div>

<div>
<h2>End of contract</h2>

<p>We offer end-of-lease de-fleeting services. If you have trucks or vans coming to the end of a contract or lease period, we can take care of de-decaling, cosmetic repairs and valeting to a very high standard.</p>
</div>

